","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 25, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhanna reported: I asked Abu Abdullah Imam Ahmad, may Allah have mercy on him, about enjoining good and forbidding evil, \u201cHow should one enjoin it?\u201d Ahmad said, \u201cOne should enjoin good with gentleness and humility. If they make him hear what he dislikes, he should not get angry such that\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41873,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/03\/28\/ibn-sireen-conscience\/","url_meta":{"origin":26911,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Sireen on Conscience: Allah makes his heart admonish him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 28, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Habib reported: Ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf Allah wills good for a servant, He appoints a preacher from his heart to command and prohibit him.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Ah\u0323mad ibn H\u0323anbal 1768 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0628\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u064d \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064b\u0627 \u062c\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33627,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/25\/ibn-abbas-confront-rulers\/","url_meta":{"origin":26911,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Rulers: Do not confront rulers if they will kill you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 25, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Jubayr reported: I asked Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cShall I enjoin good and forbid evil upon the ruler?\u201d Ibn Abbas said, \u201cIf you fear he will kill you, then no.\u201d Then, I asked him again and he said the same to me. Then, I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33842,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/12\/17\/ahmad-true-love-for-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26911,"position":3},"title":"Ahmad on Love: True love for Allah seeks no worldly benefits","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Maruwidhi reported: Imam Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked about love for the sake of Allah and he said, \u201cIt is that you not love him for the sake of some worldly benefit.\u201d Source: T\u0323abaqa\u0304t al-H\u0323ana\u0304bilah 1\/60 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0631\u0648\u0630\u064a \u0642\u062f \u0633\u0626\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0645\u0627\u0645 \u0623\u062d\u0645\u062f \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u062d\u0646\u0628\u0644\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18477,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/10\/allah-will-abandon-them\/","url_meta":{"origin":26911,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Injustice: Muslims abandoned if fail to stop oppression","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 10, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you see my nation afraid to tell the oppressor that he is an oppressor, they have been forsaken.\u201d Source: Musnad Ahmad 6784 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41191,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/19\/ibn-hanbal-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":26911,"position":5},"title":"Ahmad on Dunya: The Great Imam never speaks of worldly matters","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dawud al-Sijistani reported: The circle of Ahmad ibn Hanbal, may Allah be pleased with him, was a circle of the Hereafter, as he would not mention the affairs of the world therein. I never once saw Ahmad ibn Hanbal mentioning the world. Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 5\/291 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062f\u064e\u0627\u0648\u064f\u062f\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0